User Authentication: POST /api/register POST /api/login GET /api/user/profile
Expense Tracking: POST /api/expenses GET /api/expenses PUT /api/expenses/:id DELETE /api/expenses/:id
Budgeting: POST /api/budgets GET /api/budgets PUT /api/budgets/:id DELETE /api/budgets/:id
Financial Goals: POST /api/goals GET /api/goals PUT /api/goals/:id DELETE /api/goals/:id
Bill Reminders: POST /api/bills GET /api/bills PUT /api/bills/:id DELETE /api/bills/:id
Reports and Analytics: GET /api/reports/spending GET /api/reports/budgets GET /api/reports/goals
By organizing your project with these components and following a structured approach, you can effectively implement the key features of your Personal Finance Management App.
